<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-66-0621 </DOCNO><TEXT>A design concept is presented to retrofit a plain grating monochromatorwith a UHV-compatible water-cooling system. Included are mechanical solutionsfor the problem of adjusting the grating in relation to the synchrotronlight beam. Suggestions are made on how to optimize the system.</TEXT></DOC>